# Security & Authentication

- Auth handled by Power Platform host — no external auth libraries
- No tokens, client secrets, or connection strings in committed files
- `.env.local` (gitignored) or 1Password `op://` for local secrets
- Validate/sanitize all user input at component boundaries
- `DOMPurify` for any external HTML rendering
- Never construct dynamic URLs from user input without validation
- Pre-commit hook blocks accidental secret commits
- Connectors are the only data path (DLP)

Full details: `.github/instructions/06-security.instructions.md`
